metadata.description: Proxcity is a city simulation experience where players are immersed into a virtual world that they are in complete control of. Within this world players own their assests and have to balance essentials required to run a city. Proxcity will introduce new gameplay unlike other city simulations, as well as blockchain elements. These elements will simulate the true thrill and hardships that come with creating and maintaining a real city. Owning your land and staking it may be easy to learn, but it is a hard skill to master. As the owner of your own city you will be faced with balancing essential requirements such as: wealth, population, utilities, safety, pollution, and much more. However that is not all, you will also be faced with Proxcityâ€™s ERC20 based economy system.
